Kenneth I. Joy - Field of Interest
UC Davis
Department of Computer Science
Kenneth I. Joy
Associate Professor
Professor Joys interests are in the general area of computer graphics, especially in the subfields of image synthesis and geometric modeling.  A current focus is on free-form solid models and their integration into geometric modeling/computer graphics systems.
